"title": "8276: humility",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8276: humility",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An attitude of lowliness and obedience, grounded in the recognition of one's status before God as his creatures.</p>\n<h2>God commands humility</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:10\">JAS 4:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:3\">EXO 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:19\">PRO 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:5\">ISA 58:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:3\">ZEP 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:9-Luke14:11\">LUK 14:9–14:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:3\">ROM 12:3</a> <em>sober assessment of oneself</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:28\">1CO 1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:2\">TIT 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13\">JAS 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>God exalts the humble</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:52\">LUK 1:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:8\">2SA 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:7\">1KI 14:7</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should humble themselves before God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:6\">1PE 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:281\">2SA 22:281</a>KI <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:29\">21:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:19\">2KI 22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:6-2Chr12:7\">2CH 12:6–12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:12\">2CH 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:11\">2CH 30:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:12\">2CH 33:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:19\">2CH 33:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:27\">2CH 34:27</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:27\">18:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:9\">PSA 25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:6\">PSA 138:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:6\">PSA 147:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:34\">PRO 3:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:12\">PRO 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:6\">JAS 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:19\">ISA 29:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:15\">ISA 38:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">PRO 15:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:4\">PRO 22:4</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:13\">PSA 35:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:10\">JER 44:10</a> <em>lack of humility linked with disobedience</em></p>\n<h2>God humbles his people to renew and restore them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:9\">PSA 44:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:41\">LEV 26:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:2\">DEU 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:16\">DEU 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:39\">1KI 11:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:19\">2CH 28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:39\">PSA 107:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:1\">ISA 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:21\">2CO 12:21</a></p>\n<h2>God humbles the proud</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:14\">LUK 18:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:7\">1SA 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:11\">ISA 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:17\">ISA 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:15\">ISA 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:9\">ISA 23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:11\">ISA 25:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:5\">ISA 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:37\">DAN 4:37</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of humble people</h2>\n<h3>Outstanding individuals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:10\">GEN 32:10</a> <em>Jacob</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:16\">GEN 41:16</a> <em>Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:3\">NUM 12:3</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:21\">1SA 9:21</a> <em>Saul</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:18\">1SA 18:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:18\">2SA 7:18</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:7\">1KI 3:7</a> <em>Solomon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:30\">DAN 2:30</a> <em>Daniel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:14\">MAT 3:14</a> <em>John the Baptist</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:43\">LUK 1:43</a> <em>Elizabeth</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:48\">LUK 1:48</a> <em>Mary, the mother of Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15\">1TI 1:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:19\">ACT 20:19</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:4\">2SA 16:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:3\">PRO 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:2\">PRO 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:19\">PRO 16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:23\">PRO 29:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:22\">DAN 5:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:8\">MAT 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:27\">MAT 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:4\">MAT 18:4</a></p>\n<h2>The example of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:5–2:8</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3-Isa53:5\">ISA 53:3–53:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7-Isa53:8\">ISA 53:7–53:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:15\">JHN 12:15</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:28\">MAT 20:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:26-Luke22:27\">LUK 22:26–22:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:4\">JHN 13:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a></p>",
